19.response_text:
import time
from selenium import webdriver

#open the browser and navigate to the page
driver = webdriver.Chrome() 
driver.get("http://www.example.com/") 
time.sleep(2) 
  
#locate the text area by its id 
text_area = driver.find_element_by_id("text-area") 
  
#send the text to the text area using send_keys() method 
text_area.send_keys("This is an example of autotyping text in Django.") 

 #close the browser  
driver.close()
